<section class="hero edge-bottom">
    <div class="container">
            <img class="bg" src="/images/home/hero.jpg" alt="The Dual Threats of Food<br/>and Plastic Waste">

        <h1 class="blocky">
            <span>The Dual Threats of Food<br/>and Plastic Waste</span>
        </h1>
        <div class="rte body"><p>In our quest to nurture the leaders of tomorrow, we confront not just the challenge of education but also the preservation of the environment they will inherit. Food and plastic waste represent two of the most pressing environmental issues of our time. Addressing these issues isn't just a matter of conservation; it's a moral imperative to ensure a livable world for future generations.</p>
</div>
    </div>
</section>
<section class="image-with-text right">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12 col-md-4" >
                    <img class="image w-100" src="/images/home/kids-food-lunchbox.jpg" alt="Uniting for a Waste-Wise Future!">
            </div>

            <div class="text col-12 col-md-8 mt-4 mt-md-0">
                <h3 class="blocky blocky-subtitle"><span>From Classroom to Community</span></h3>
                <h2 class="h1">Uniting for a Waste-Wise Future!</h2>
                <h2 class="subtitle">The Call to Action for Every Teacher and Student</h2>
                    <div class="rte"><p>The fight against food and plastic waste is a battle that schools are uniquely positioned to lead. By harnessing the power of education, innovation, and community, we can cultivate a culture of sustainability that extends far beyond the classroom walls. This is our opportunity to nourish minds while protecting our precious planet—let's embrace it together.</p>
</div>
                    <div class="pt-4">
                        <a href="/make-change/challenge/" class="btn-arrow">Make change</a>
                    </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<section class="image-with-text left">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12 col-md-4" >
                    <img class="image w-100" src="/images/home/bag-with-food.jpg" alt="Lessons for a Zero-Waste World">
            </div>

            <div class="text col-12 col-md-8 mt-4 mt-md-0">
                <h3 class="blocky blocky-subtitle"><span>What works well</span></h3>
                <h2 class="h1">Lessons for a Zero-Waste World</h2>
                
                    <div class="rte"><p>In our commitment to fostering a sustainable future, we present "What works well", a comprehensive hub designed to equip educators and students with the knowledge and tools needed to combat the dual threats of food and plastic waste.</p>
</div>
                    <div class="pt-4">
                        <a href="/what-works-well/" class="btn-arrow">What works well</a>
                    </div>
            </div>
